OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778073067
OL,3,CBan early morning pre-flight pints at
OL,4,Cairports, Ryanair boss says
OL,6,FAirports should be banned from serving
OL,7,Falcohol to passengers before early
OL,8,Fmorning flights to reduce disruptive
OL,9,Fbehaviour onboard aircraft, Ryanair
OL,10,Fboss Michael O'Leary has said.
OL,12,FThe budget airline's chief executive
OL,13,Fsaid Ryanair is forced to divert an
OL,14,Faverage of nearly one flight every day
OL,15,Fbecause of bad behaviour onboard, up
OL,16,Ffrom one a week a decade ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
