PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778073067
OL,3,CBan early morning pre-flight pints at
OL,4,Cairports, Ryanair boss says
OL,6,F"It's becoming a real challenge for
OL,7,Fall airlines," he told the Times. "I
OL,8,Ffail to understand why anybody in
OL,9,Fairport bars is serving people at five
OL,10,For six o'clock in the morning.
OL,12,F"Who needs to be drinking beer at that
OL,13,Ftime?"
OL,15,FNormally bars and pubs and other
OL,16,Fvenues selling alcohol are required to
OL,17,Ffollow restrictions on opening hours,
OL,18,Fbased on their licenses, but these do
OL,19,Fnot apply to airside bars.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@NO]oD@cOUtD@AOUuD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
