PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1778073067
OL,3,CBan early morning pre-flight pints at
OL,4,Cairports, Ryanair boss says
OL,6,F"There should be no alcohol served at
OL,7,Fairports outside (those) licensing
OL,8,Fhours," Mr O'Leary said, adding that
OL,9,FRyanair rarely served more than two
OL,10,Fdrinks to a passenger during one of
OL,11,Fits flight.
OL,13,FMr O'Leary reiterated his previous
OL,14,Fcalls for a two-drink limit to be
OL,15,Fintroduced at airports as well.
