OL,3,CBan early morning pre-flight pints at
OL,4,Cairports, Ryanair boss says
OL,6,FIn January last year, Ryanair
OL,7,Fannounced it had started taking legal
OL,8,Faction to recover losses against
OL,9,Fdisruptive passengers when they forced
OL,10,Fa flight to be diverted.
OL,12,FIt said it filed legal proceedings
OL,13,Fagainst a passenger in Ireland to seek
OL,14,F15,000 euros (#12,500) in damages
OL,15,Frelated to a flight from Dublin to
OL,16,FLanzarote.
